headline: Why Uber (UBER) Shares Are Sliding Today
summary: Shares of ride sharing and on-demand delivery platform Uber (NYSE:UBER) fell 4.3% in the morning session after the company lost a UK Supreme Court appeal regarding a value-added tax (VAT) on its rivals.
